      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "For sale: A driver-spec 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six and a proper 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. This example is mechanically sorted, featuring a fully overhauled VANOS system and updated rod bearings to address the platform's critical longevity requirements. The chassis is reinforced at the rear subframe points, paired with a factory M-variable limited-slip differential that delivers exceptional power delivery through the twisties. It sits on refreshed suspension components with upgraded dampers for precise damping and rebound. While it shows the honest patina of a car that has been driven as intended, the drivetrain remains tight, linear, and responsive. A turn-key performance icon for the purist.",
